cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Trust Identity Protocol (TIP): An Open Standard for Verified Human Identity and Content Provenance on the Internet"
message: "If you reference or build on the Trust Identity Protocol in academic, regulatory, or commercial work, please cite the canonical whitepaper using the metadata below. The Zenodo DOI is the recommended persistent identifier."
